data.description: Welcome to Your New Home! This delightful single-story residence offers ADA accessibility, ensuring an inclusive and comfortable living environment. The front yard welcomes visitors with its mature trees, casting refreshing shade and offering a friendly environment. This home features a recently upgraded roof, it boasts three spacious bedrooms, a well-appointed bathroom, and a separate laundry room for convenience. The converted covered garage serves as a versatile supplementary living space, catering to diverse needs, and perfect for added entertainment.  Meanwhile, the spacious backyard offers a great deal of shade from the well-established trees and comes complete with a storage shed ideal for outdoor entertaining and relaxation. This turnkey home is ready for immediate occupancy, combining functionality with natural beauty.
